{"tid":1488963,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"如果以後集會過100萬人，我都唔裸跑","createTime":"2019-08-19T17:59:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-20T01:12:16.000Z","uid":309775,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"5b54b1e9a0e5cf40013798afb1741f1bd0159280","tid":1488963,"uid":309775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T17:59:00.000Z","msg":"初次開post兼p牌，我比較不善言辭，希望大家高抬貴手，唔好屌咁大力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n希望大家<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">暫停開「如果...我就...」嘅post</span></span><br />\n<br />\n我明白今日大家睇兩位巴打找數真漢子係好興奮，我睇live都心肝仔砰砰跳<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，但係希望各位記得，狗係好撚陰濕嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n今次咁多巴絲去到現場睇巴打找數，萬一下次有狗扮巴打開post話如果學生集會過5萬人佢就去清水灣JJ插沙，又有成村人走咗過去，咁就一鑊熟<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n為咗保護自己、保護手足，建議大家暫時唔好再開呢類post住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n等成件事完咗之後再瘋狂裸跑啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c4fcf0e478783633dc4aca971656e364b320b2b","tid":1488963,"uid":309775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T18:01:15.000Z","msg":"p牌仔推唔郁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"939f350eb31b28f2e5700fd20e2a1f5bebbc191e","tid":1488963,"uid":290804,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T18:08:25.000Z","msg":"&lt;821&gt;咁撚大件事冇人講 全撚同我入嚟！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1488892\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1488892</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n件事完咗就算"},{"pid":"f10b0ea7db614403a18ee797f6f7fee3c7ffc61e","tid":1488963,"uid":180606,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T01:12:16.000Z","msg":"裸跑無罪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}